      • solveReport

        public java.lang.Boolean solveReport​(Report report,
                                     java.lang.Boolean type,
                                     java.lang.Boolean explicit)
        Method to solve a report. The parameter 'report' indicates te report to solve. 'type' indicates the way in which the report is solved, if it is false, then the song is deleted, if it's true, the song remains. Finally, 'explicit' tell us if after solving the report, the song changes to explicit content or not.
        Parameters:
        report -
        type -
        explicit -
        Returns:
        if the report was solved correctly
